Hello and welcome to our application! We care about your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. Please read the following privacy policy to understand how we collect and use the information we gather.

**Information We Collect:**
When using the application, we collect information related to the services you request.
We gather non-personal information, such as operational and statistical data.

**How We Use the Information:**
We use the information we collect to provide services and enhance your experience with the application.
We do not share your information with third parties without your consent.

**Security:**
We take security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access.
